# UI Conventions

## Component Library

- Use **shadcn/ui** components from `@/components/ui/` (Button, Input, Form, Dialog, Label)
- shadcn style: **new-york**, base color: **slate**, CSS variables enabled
- Add new shadcn components via `npx shadcn@latest add <name>`

## Tailwind CSS 4

- Config in `src/app/globals.css` using `@theme inline` block
- Custom colors: `--color-main: #003562`, `--color-semantic-info: #0EA5E9`, `--color-safety-orange: #FF6A00`
- Background: `#F1F5F9`, protected pages: `bg-[#E8F4FF]`

## Mobile-First

- Touch targets: minimum **44px** (h-11 / h-12)
- Font sizes: minimum **16px** on mobile inputs (prevents iOS zoom)
- Use responsive prefixes: base → `sm:` → `md:` → `lg:`

## Vietnamese UI Text

- All user-facing labels, placeholders, error messages in **Vietnamese**
- Code (variable names, comments) in **English**
- Examples: "Đăng nhập", "Đăng ký", "Mật khẩu", "Trang chủ"

## Form Pattern

```tsx
// Always use React Hook Form + Zod
const form = useForm<MyInput>({
  resolver: zodResolver(mySchema),
  defaultValues: { ... },
})

// Wrap in shadcn Form
<Form {...form}>
  <form onSubmit={form.handleSubmit(onSubmit)}>
    <FormField control={form.control} name="field" render={...} />
  </form>
</Form>
```

## Animations

- Page/form transitions: Framer Motion (`AnimatePresence` + `motion.div`)
- CSS keyframes in `globals.css` for simpler effects (shine, tab-enter)
